 The Best of Mbombela Readers’ Choice Awards took place on Wednesday at Emnotweni Arena.At the prestigious event, the best in Mbombela were awarded for their excellent work. The public chose their favourite eating place, shopping centre, schools and all manner of things. Every year thousands of voters choose their favourite businesses which are crowned the best of Mbombela. ALSO READ:Mbombela’s best as voted for by the public announced All the categories were announced and all the winners got to celebrate their memorable moment. Here is the list of winners:  Lowvelder thanked Stabilis, AVS Hire, MO’s Studio, Emnotweni Arena, Montana Garden Pavilion and DGB for their support in making the event a huge success. 